lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps won two gold medals on Tuesday, avenging his 200 meters butterfly defeat from the London Olympics and then anchoring the U.S. 4x200 freestyle team to victory on a night of high drama and emotion in the pool.

headline.main: Two More Golds for Phelps, Hosszu and Ledecky March On
